text: Ravenswaaij is a village in the Dutch province of Gelderland. It is a part of the municipality of Buren, and lies about 10 km northwest of Tiel. The village Ravenswaaij has a population of around 190.Statistics Netherlands (CBS), Statline: Kerncijfers wijken en buurten 2003-2005. As of 1 January 2005. The statistical area "Ravenswaaij", which also can include the surrounding countryside, has a population of around 410. ==References== Category:Populated places in Gelderland Category:Buren
title: Ravenswaaij
